title: Robert Hansen: The Butcher Baker
description:
Former FBI agent and criminal profiler Candice DeLong delves into the case of Robert Hansen, the Butcher Baker. Robert raped over 30 women and killed, at least, 17 victims - setting them loose in the frozen Alaska terrain and hunting them down like animals.
